# React Native + Expo + TanStack Query + Zustand + RHF + Zod + styled-components

## Cursor Rules / AI Guardrails

---

## 1️⃣ General Architecture Rules

### ✅ Follow Feature-Based Folder Structure

```
src/
├── app/                                                      # Expo Router (routing layer)
│   ├── _layout.tsx                                           # Root layout + providers
│   └── (tabs)/
│       ├── _layout.tsx                                       # Tab navigator
│       ├── screen1.tsx                                       # Route to feature screen
│       ├── screen2.tsx
│       └── screen3.tsx

├── features/                                                 # Business domains
│   └── <feature-name>/
│       ├── api.ts                                            # Feature API calls
│       ├── types.ts                                          # TypeScript types
│       ├── store.ts                                          # Zustand slice for feature state
│       ├── schema.ts                                         # Zod validation schemas
│       ├── ui/                                               # UI layer
│       │   └── <role-name>/
│       │           ├── screens/
│       │           │   └── <FeatureScreen>.tsx
│       │           └── components/
│       │               └── <FeatureComponent>.tsx
│       └── index.ts                                          # Public feature API
├── shared/                                                   # Generic reusable utilities and UI
│   ├── ui/<SharedComponent>.tsx
│   ├── hooks/<sharedHook>.ts
│   ├── lib/<shared-lib>.ts
│   ├── utils/<utility>.ts
│   └── theme/
│       ├── colors.ts
│       └── spacing.ts

└── assets/                                                   # Images, fonts, icons
    ├── images/
    ├── fonts/
    └── icons/
```

**Rules:**

- Keep logic inside feature folders
- Avoid cross-feature imports
- Shared code must go into `/lib`, `/components`, or `/utils`

